SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]

2024-09-29 22:23:32.205 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (14ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]
2024-09-29 23:39:28.428 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Slug], [c].[Status]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]

) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]

2024-09-29 23:48:24.602 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (65ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[OriginName], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId]
